{"tid":1297686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致為還在努力堅持、愛香港的朋友，","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T17:27:44.000Z","uid":202183,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f0485b029c2c5b90a398082bd7f2037e6403a6","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"今日夜晚過咗去海富探一探絕食明志嘅絕食者，之後去咗連儂牆嗰邊幾位烈士嘅路祭。<br />\n見到有位婆婆清理緊喺地上嘅鮮花，佢見我係後生仔，佢就俾咗一張memo紙我，婆婆話佢睇到memo紙嘅內容佢好感動，所以婆婆叫我影低、掟上網，俾大家知道一位喺金鐘默默獻花嘅一個女仔嘅心聲。<br />\n<br />\n「致 為強權、反送中犧牲了的朋友們，<br />\n對不起，唯一可以為你們做的只能是送上不會凋謝的白色假花，願你們安息，願你們只是站在高處，想成為第一個看見希望的人。<br />\n<br />\n致 為還在努力堅持、愛香港的朋友，一個都不可以再少，齊進齊退，一齊堅持，要親眼看見香港人用愛和團結打倒強權！！」<br />\n<br />\n婆婆話，佢覺得獻花都要俾人清走，佢覺得好心up，所以拜託我喺網上傳開呢個獻假花嘅女仔嘅故事，同時，又問我梁先生嘅葬禮係幾時，佢話為到呢件事好痛心，所以一定要去。<br />\n<br />\n婆婆亦都分享，佢話班「魔警」全部都係失去良知、兇殘、恐怖，佢又問我宜家旺角情況點，仲有冇「魔警」亂咁打到人頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n最後，想引用2015年法國恐襲，一個爸爸向死者獻花嘅時候，對佢個仔講嘅一句說話：「They might have guns, but we have flowers.」<br />\n面對克警、面對極權，或許他們有殺人嘅武器，但是讓我們一同舉起鮮花捍衛自己的民主、自由。<br />\n<br />\n四位烈士，一路好走。<br />\n香港人，一個都不能少。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsF4p3F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzsF4p3F.png&h=5eaf5d39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d62e4ad8cf7e61d083645930714cfed12ffdb39a","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:23:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"3642b99bcc45ac5679041272925452cd5324fec4","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要見律師"},{"pid":"09b3a9c28c61939a73c3799dd71f672004bab07f","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b238fee5f791d8c60be7be4add4098a38caeb3","tid":1297686,"uid":113148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊撐落去<br />\n<br />\nWe have flowers"},{"pid":"1b88769958f942235d21748d1cc9f546c6180679","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:32:35.000Z","msg":"Pish<br />\n我哋要一齊親愛看見香港人用愛和團結打倒強權！"},{"pid":"43a28987675d6649c1289b7946e8a420bcc8efae","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"fc334aa087cf55a53807f5e85b66856689cc5639","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"5a39e209e45d691edf3076ea35884143bcb0fd29","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"a2b9d32d690f254304c6211cb6309895c410ef63","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"9d2c22acfff1d08e262b69c01b59df14888ce144","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:45:32.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"ee5b1e2f637c01b44ebb7be7d2289cfcf37d9f51","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:51:18.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c6aebb74b5594aafe5b35c46fb3a65d8bb7345","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:11:39.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"aa9fa52e876f9a9db09fcbde95b468e4e5e30c68","tid":1297686,"uid":202183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20